---
title: Striploin Steak and Blueberry-Balsamic Reduction with Asparagus Almandine and Goat Cheese Mash
description: Perfectly seared steak goes oh-so-well with our balsamic blueberry and peppercorn sauce in this date-worthy weeknight dinner. Paired with goat cheese mash and seasonal asparagus, you might want to lick the plate!
